      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<style>\n.faq-section {\n  background:#ebecf0;\n  max-width: 950px;\n  margin: 0 auto 70px auto;\n  padding:50px 30px;\n  border-radius:14px;\n}\n\n.faq-section h2 {\n  text-align:center;\n  font-size:34px;\n  margin-bottom:40px;\n}\n\n.faq-item {\n  background:#fff;\n  padding:22px;\n  border-left:4px solid #111;\n  border-radius:8px;\n  margin-bottom:20px;\n}\n\n.faq-item h3 {\n  font-size:19px;\n  margin-bottom:10px;\n}\n\n@media (max-width: 900px) {\n  .faq-section { padding: 35px 18px; }\n}\n<\/style>\n\n<section class=\"faq-section\">\n<h2>MacBook Repair London FAQs<\/h2>\n\n<div class=\"faq-item\">\n<h3><strong>Where is iCorrect located in London?<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>We're based at 12 Margaret Street, London W1W 8JQ  -  a short walk from Oxford Circus and Regent Street. Walk-ins are welcome. Mail-in repair is also available across the UK.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"faq-item\">\n<h3><strong>How long does MacBook repair take?<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Most repairs are completed within 48 hours. Screen replacements and battery swaps are often same-day. Logic board diagnostics and liquid damage repairs typically take 3–5 working days. Express slots are available.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"faq-item\">\n<h3><strong>Do you offer a no-fix no-fee guarantee?<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Yes. If we can't fix your MacBook, you don't pay for the repair. Diagnostic fees may apply for logic board assessments if the board cannot be repaired.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"faq-item\">\n<h3><strong>Can you repair MacBook logic boards in London?<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>Yes  -  this is one of our core specialisms. We carry out component-level microchip repair on MacBook logic boards, including power circuit failures, liquid damage corrosion, and charging IC faults.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<div class=\"faq-item\">\n<h3><strong>What MacBook models do you repair?<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>We repair all MacBook models from 2016 onwards, including MacBook Air, MacBook Pro 13\", 14\", 15\", and 16\". We can also assist older models for battery and data recovery work.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<\/section>\n\n<script type=\"application\/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https:\/\/schema.org\",\n  \"@type\": \"LocalBusiness\",\n  \"name\": \"iCorrect\",\n  \"image\": \"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0674\/1952\/0525\/files\/MacBook_Repair.png\",\n  \"url\": \"https:\/\/www.icorrect.co.uk\/pages\/macbook-repair-london\",\n  \"telephone\": \"+442080049995\",\n  \"address\": {\n    \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n    \"streetAddress\": \"12 Margaret Street\",\n    \"addressLocality\": \"London\",\n    \"postalCode\": \"W1W 8JQ\",\n    \"addressCountry\": \"GB\"\n  },\n  \"geo\": {\n    \"@type\": \"GeoCoordinates\",\n    \"latitude\": 51.5175,\n    \"longitude\": -0.1418\n  },\n  \"openingHoursSpecification\": [\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"OpeningHoursSpecification\",\n      \"dayOfWeek\": [\"Monday\",\"Tuesday\",\"Wednesday\",\"Thursday\",\"Friday\"],\n      \"opens\": \"09:00\",\n      \"closes\": \"18:00\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"priceRange\": \"££\",\n  \"description\": \"MacBook repair specialists in London. Screens, batteries, keyboards, liquid damage, logic board repairs. 2-year warranty. Same-day express available.\"\n}\n<\/script>",
